[Affected versions]:
- Nightly 62.0a1;

[Affected platforms]:
- Win 10x64;
- Ubuntu 16.04LTS;
- MacOS 10.13.4. 

[Steps to reproduce]:
1. Launch Firefox;
2. Add the following link and press Enter on the keyboard: https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/62.0a1/tracking-protection/start/?step=3
3. Click inside the address bar;
4. Press on the left-right arrows on the keyboard.

[Expected result]:
- Cursor moves left-right.

[Actual result]:
- Cursor does not move left-right.

[Regression range]:
- Not a regression since its also reproducible on the build where the feature was introduced, Nightly 2018-06-01.

[Additional notes]:
- attached screen-cast with the issue;
- pressing the up key selects the Cookies clear button;
